Controller Mapping for PS4
Left Stick: X, Y
  Up: -
  Down: +
  Left: -
  Right: +

Right Stick: U, V
  Up: -
  Down: +
  Left: -
  Right: +

PovX:
  Up: -
  Down: +
  Left: -
  Right: +

Buttons:
  Button0: X
  Button1: O
  Button2: Tri
  Button3: Sqr
  Button4: L1
  Button5: R1
  Button6: L2
  Button7: R2
  Button8: Share
  Button9: Options
  Button10: PS button
  Button11: LS
  Button12: RS
